<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.2.6">
<l>veñciṉa vēḻam maruppo citta vēntarko lēnti ḻaiyār maṉattai</l>
<l>tañcuṭai yāḷar kolyā ṉaṟiyēṉ tāmaraik kaṇka ḷirunta vāṟu</l>
<l>kañcaṉai yañca muṉkāl vicaitta kāḷaiya rāvar kaṇṭār vaṇaṅkum</l>
<l>añcaṉa māma laiyē yumoppa raccō voruva raḻaki yavā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is he the warrior who broke the tusk of the cruel, angry elephant?</l>
<l>Is he the one with a refuge for the hearts of bejeweled ladies?</l>
<l rend="indent">I don’t know. The way his lotus eyes are!</l>
<l>He became the youth who raged long ago so that Kamsa feared.</l>
<l>He is like a great collyrium mountain which those who see him adore.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, the way that one is handsome!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
